# AhaDiff

Use AhaDiff after meaningful code changes to turn the current diff into
verified learn-back artifacts.

Preferred commands:

- `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD`
- `ahadiff learn --staged`
- `ahadiff quiz <run_id>`
- `ahadiff review`
- `ahadiff verify <run_id>`
- `ahadiff improve <run_id>`
- `ahadiff serve`

Prefer generated explanations backed by verified claims and file-line evidence.
Treat `.ahadiff/review.sqlite`, `.ahadiff/runs/`, and `prompts/` as local
AhaDiff state. Keep provider secrets in environment variables and do not commit
private `.ahadiff/` audit logs or local provider endpoints.
